description=AI-driven adaptive thermal throttling for POCO F6 (peridot). v2.3.0: Advanced intelligent features (Predictive Forecasting, Dynamic Weighting, Per-Game Profiles, Snapshots, etc). Bootloop protection, self-calibration, smart battery charge control, suspend/screen-off cooling, and auto-gaming network/touch tweaks. Prevents frame drops while keeping the device cool without degrading UI smoothness.
